{"type":"answer","id":59231,"parentType":"question","parentId":13725,"uid":8751,"contents":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/tie-qia-90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-07<br>\n说的不错，但是古希腊古罗马呢……<br>\n<center>1</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>踩</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<br>\n13 条回复<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ebf14e8edc630244e1f4aa52872c50b5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e8b33fa221f7298a35d4072468179df_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e8b33fa221f7298a35d4072468179df_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/ebf14e8edc630244e1f4aa52872c50b5\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">吟赏烟霞</a>&nbsp;(作者)&nbsp;回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-07<br>\n那边的我不熟，我主要看的是中哲。🤕体系不同，抱歉了啊。😕<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>踩</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fb82cf7451d82f65e3f4bb5c0028a39_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fb82cf7451d82f65e3f4bb5c0028a39_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">聆听者</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-09<br>\n你拿环地中海地区和半封闭大陆比？自然经济时代，地理环境因素对文明的影响是第一位的<br>\n<br>\n<center>2</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>踩</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">聆听者</a>2019-04-09<br>\n没能超越地理环境所囿，所谓的“先贤”是否要打点折扣？<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fb82cf7451d82f65e3f4bb5c0028a39_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3fb82cf7451d82f65e3f4bb5c0028a39_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">聆听者</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-09<br>\n自然经济时代能够提出超越地理环境影响的制度解决方案，那不叫先贤，那叫超人<br>\n<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f8c5ac894bb04565cdcf024210b9d7b6\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">聆听者</a>2019-04-09<br>\n你觉得没折扣，我觉得有折扣，就这样吧~<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a8db728feb150128ecc14900aed948ae\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-03b42d62450ffcb05428b958512bea22_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-03b42d62450ffcb05428b958512bea22_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/a8db728feb150128ecc14900aed948ae\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">安分的小安民</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-10<br>\n古希腊罗马是因为特殊的自然环境，只是对社会条件的适应，中国当时帝制也是对中国社会条件的适应，历史不能一概而论<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/da8e974dc_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/da8e974dc_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「已注销」</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-13<br>\n你这种折扣就跟知乎上常见的过誉问题一样，有树靶子自己打的嫌疑。<br>\n<br>\n正经学术界从来没觉得孔孟乃至其它先贤的思想有多完美多超脱——哪怕是两千年的学术界。<br>\n<center>2</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「已注销」</a>2019-04-13<br>\n我觉得有折扣还不行吗？你不会有病吧……<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/da8e974dc_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/da8e974dc_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「已注销」</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-04-13<br>\n因为“折扣”必然是相对于某个更高标的评价而言。但这个高标的评价很大程度上是你和其他人自己意淫出来的。<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「已注销」</a>2019-04-13<br>\n你觉得没有折扣又何尝不是意淫呢……以后说别人的时候想想自己<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/c731be7115f8d88b5fc621cb0b6fe729\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b8cc10d7951c91eb09749f769acbdcf_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-2b8cc10d7951c91eb09749f769acbdcf_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/c731be7115f8d88b5fc621cb0b6fe729\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">内阁小学士</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>2019-05-12<br>\n一年前我还会称你这种人为过分的完美主义。一年后我觉得你就是一个**<br>\n<center>1</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2dde913336bfc87694d856c1221601dd_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/f89023914c16baaa97a09ddf3eb5c841\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">铁卡</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/c731be7115f8d88b5fc621cb0b6fe729\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">内阁小学士</a>2019-05-12<br>\n一年前我对你这种人还能包容，现在我觉得你就是个××——盗版你一下[微笑]<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n<center>举报</center><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/281d197580f54f2cd41ce93fe57ec6f9\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"></a><a href=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d81d879be6deb2e3f890deaaa7aa07c0_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-d81d879be6deb2e3f890deaaa7aa07c0_s.jpg?source=06d4cd63</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/281d197580f54f2cd41ce93fe57ec6f9\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">好无聊</a>回复<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/932158a59c80a66c82cd4d0fe1a58b90\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">「已注销」</a>2019-05-31<br>\n王阳明算一个，知行合一，致良知，中国人要是有一半能学进去，早推翻帝国了，被小日本学了去了，明治维新瞅瞅去，先贤不是你能评论的<br>\n<center>赞</center><br>\n<center>回复</center><br>\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br>\n以上的评论是知乎上对于第一个回答“在那个时代下，君主制是最好的选择”这个观点的回复。<br>\n我觉得比起回答的正文，评论看起来更有意思。","date":"2020-12-19","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}